I get the text from the "DISPLAYED COUNTRY" button

I click on "DISPLAYED COUNTRY" button
I get the text from the phone number prefix on the "First SignIn Screen"
I check that the application text: "+48" is equals to expected value: "+48"
I click on "PHONE NUMBER" input
I enter the phone number "732223116" in the input
I click on "LET'S GO" button
I check that the "Sign Up Screen" is displayed
I click on "FIRST NAME" input
I enter the first name "Dominik" in the input
I click on "LAST NAME" input
I enter the last name "Doe" in the input
I click on "EMAIL ADDRESS" input
I enter the email "dominik.doe@test.com" in the input
I click on "COUNTRY" input
I check that the "Country List Pane" is displayed
I click on "SWEDEN" country button
I click on "PASSWORD" input
I enter the password "#Test123" in the input
I swipe on the device screen to the "DOWN"
I click on "COMMERCIAL" checkbox
I click on "TOS" checkbox
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I check that the "Passcode Step Screen" is displayed
I wait for the OTP code to be sent to my mailbox
I enter the OTP passcode "605921" in the input
I click on "COMPLETE SIGN UP" button
